{
  "stem": "8892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I cannot-- that picture I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because as far as you could see your eyes-- and here I am wandering as a kid, just faces of women.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You don't know who they are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some would talk to you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "While some you didn't want to talk to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You just wandered aimlessly and wandered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One day I wandered towards the kitchen of the smell-- which was opposite end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Not where the field was, where everybody gathered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But you couldn't go back to the barrack, by the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "During the day, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You went only when the food was coming, afternoon, again at night time, I mean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And again the they had to be in platz, and they counted you again for hours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if anyone was missing, you were punished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You didn't get the food like 5 or 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You got it after.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't even know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I think once or twice they took us to a community bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I-- I mean a-- a shower place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But when they took us, and we had to get out of our barracks, or our lager, the C lager, you were always ready that this is the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You were already ready that you're not going to come back to that barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we were fortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were really like, once a month, I think, or once in three weeks, we stripped and we showered, and we put back the same filthy clothes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, one day I wandered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm going towards the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there is a beautiful, gorgeous blue water swimming pool, back of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I stand with the dress on, whatever, I don't think I took anything off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I jump in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I start swimming.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
